metadata.name: Language of another world
metadata.description:
A collaboration between @MickeyFalzone & @ApricotBlossomD

France, Provence, Valensole, 4th Jul 2015

Only the buzzing sound of the bees was breaking the silence, thousands of them amongst the rows of lavender.

The surreal glow of the lantern looked beautiful on Danila’s face and this night view of Valensole has always been one of my favorites.

On top of Michele’s image Marion added a textured frame made with A.R, elements of a constellation sky, hand painted Moon flowers and a Luna moth.

Moon flowers symbolize blossoming in dark times, potential growth of our personality when faced with the hardship of our lives.

The nocturnal Luna moth represents our need to “find the light” a symbolic quest for truth and knowledge, intuition and increased awareness.

The color white in the elements represents purity, innocence, goodness, light and natural elegance.

This NFT comes with special unlockable augmented reality content to be released only to the 1st owner at the end of the auction.
